# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# UOR OS — Environment Variables
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
#
# Copy this file to .env and fill in the values you need.
#
#   cp .env.example .env
#
# ── Required: NONE ─────────────────────────────────────────────────
# The core shell (desktop, dock, kernel, knowledge graph, sovereign
# boot) runs fully offline with zero configuration.
#
# ── Optional: Remote features ──────────────────────────────────────
# Uncomment and set these to enable AI oracle, encrypted messenger,
# cloud sync, and edge functions.

# VITE_SUPABASE_URL=https://your-project.supabase.co
# VITE_SUPABASE_PUBLISHABLE_KEY=your-anon-key

# If you only have a project ID (without a full URL):
# VITE_SUPABASE_PROJECT_ID=your-project-id
